bucketFolder.description: Custom S3 Bucket Object prefix for intermediate storage.

bucketName.description: Custom S3 Bucket name for intermediate storage.

encryptionMode.description: The server-side encryption mode that you want to encrypt your intermediate .csv object files copied to S3. Defaults to `SSE_S3`. Valid values are `SSE_S3` and `SSE_KMS`.

serverSideEncryptionKmsKeyId.description: ARN or Id of KMS Key to use when `encryption_mode` is `SSE_KMS`.

serviceAccessRoleArn.description: Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the IAM Role with permissions to read from or write to the S3 Bucket for intermediate storage.
